    ****REPLACE THE FOLLOWING WITH SIMILAR INFORMATION. Class for a ML-ARAM classifier.

    * Valid options are:

    -P
    Use a different generalization value.

    -K
    Use ML rankings to class.

    -V
    Define the number of voters.
